===Noun===
'''arrow''' (''plural'' '''[[arrows]]''')
#A [[projectile]] consisting of a shaft, a point and a tail with stabilizing fins that is shot from a [[bow]].
#A [[sign]] or [[symbol]] more or less shaped like this projectile, used to indicate the [[direction]] in which it seems to point (like this <math>\to</math>).
#{{graphtheory}} A [[directed edge]].

